Ana Maria Salazar is reporting from Hermosillo, Mexico where 43 children died
in a fire at a day care facility. [She writes about those who gathered at a
mass to mourn this loss
[es].](http://www.anamariasalazar.com/2009/06/hermosillo-llora-por-sus-
hijos.html)She also asks, “how can this be avoided so that it won't happen
again?”

